title: The Star-Touched Queen
description: Its hard to imagine a world without A Light in the Attic. This now-classic collection of poetry and drawings from Shel Silverstein celebrates its 20th anniversary with this special edition. Silversteins humorous and creative verse can amuse the dowdiest of readers.
